<topic id='attribute_activity_location_type_code.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: ACTIVITY LOCATION TYPE CODE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The type of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_location">LOCATION</xref>
 for an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
where 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 are seen                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
where 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 are provided or                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
from which requests for 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 are sent.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>Notes:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <p>
The following National Code is 
                          <b>only</b>
 valid for the 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_community_services_data_set">Community Services Data Set</xref>, 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet"
                     keyref="dataset_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_data_set">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Data Set</xref>, 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_maternity_services_data_set">Maternity Services Data Set</xref>
 and 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_mental_health_services_data_set">Mental Health Services Data Set</xref>. Users of other data sets must map National Code G04 locally to other appropriate 
                          <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_activity_location_type_code">ACTIVITY LOCATION TYPE CODES</xref>
 for the purposes of flowing data:                </p>
            <ul>
               <li>
                  <p>
G04 
                                      <i>'Integrated 
                                          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                              keyref="business_definition_care_home_without_nursing">Care Home Without Nursing</xref>
 and 
                                          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                              keyref="business_definition_care_home_with_nursing">Care Home With Nursing</xref>'</i>
                  </p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
The following National Codes have been introduced for the 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet"
                     keyref="dataset_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_data_set">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Data Set</xref>
 and 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_mental_health_services_data_set">Mental Health Services Data Set</xref>
               <b>only</b>
 to add further granularity to National Code M04 
                          <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution">Young Offender Institution</xref>'</i>. However, National Code M04 is still valid for the 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet"
                     keyref="dataset_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_data_set">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Data Set</xref>
 and 
                          <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_mental_health_services_data_set">Mental Health Services Data Set</xref>
 where extra detail cannot be collected:                </p>
            <ul>
               <li>
                  <p>
M06 
                                      <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                              keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution__15-17_">Young Offender Institution (15-17)</xref>'</i>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>
M07 
                                      <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                              keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution__18-21_">Young Offender Institution (18-21)</xref>'.                            </i>
                  </p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
         <b>
Further information on the groupings and scope of each 
                  <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_activity_location_type_code">ACTIVITY LOCATION TYPE CODE</xref>
 is provided at: 
                  <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                  keyref="supporting_definition_activity_location_type_codes">Activity Location Type Codes</xref>.            </b>
      </p>
  </div>
</body>
